        Constructor for a TileProperty with an unknown drawID (a new TileProperty).

        The drawID should be assigned by the Grand Source of All DrawIDs.

        Parameters:
        location - The Tile this property is attached to.
        context - the Context within which this Property may com.meteorcode.pathway.model.Property.eval scripts. This should be the script context of whomever owns the property.
